units metal

atom_style atomic
read_data data/water.data

pair_style metatomic pet-mad-xs-v1.5.0.pt device cpu
pair_coeff * * 8 1

neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify one 5000

run_style verlet
timestep 0.0005

thermo 10
thermo_style custom step temp pe ke etotal

velocity all create 300.0 87287 mom yes rot yes dist gaussian
fix thermostat all langevin 300.0 300.0 0.1 928733 zero yes
fix integration all nve

dump trajectory all custom 10 conservative.lammpstrj id type element x y z
dump_modify trajectory sort id element O H

run 400
